{"tid":2092642,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不愧是女團代表！TWICE 刷新女團專輯銷量紀錄","createTime":"2020-07-03T10:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T09:24:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"518cd806985877ba3da3d33c4fd2abafbe7914fc","tid":2092642,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"出道至今屢次創下銷量佳績的 TWICE，最近又憑著新專輯〈MORE &amp; MORE〉締造新紀錄啦！<br />\n<br />\n根據 Gaon Chart 的數據顯示，TWICE 在 6 月 1 日發行的第九張迷你專輯〈MORE &amp; MORE〉，到昨天為止已賣出約 563,000 張，就此寫下 Gaon Chart 史上最高的女團唱片銷量紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n〈MORE &amp; MORE〉早在預售階段時，便已賣出逾 50 萬張而達成「半百銷量」；在發行滿一週後，TWICE 除了刷新自己出道以來的最高首週銷量（332,416 張），還首度打入告示牌兩百強專輯榜。<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，從 2015 年出道至今，TWICE 光是在韓國便已經賣出超過 526 萬張唱片，若加上在日本的銷量，則已賣出多達 880 萬張唱片！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"020d1ca2a7b0c07a6d057162a2e4b5a010e4a290","tid":2092642,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_1474dc36e23bc61c8ae901e0e7f43cbc/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-07-03/128084-853307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_1474dc36e23bc61c8ae901e0e7f43cbc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-07-03%2F128084-853307.png&h=7058ae57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9bfb950299295e363a972add5b8cf8a9/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-07-03/128084-853308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9bfb950299295e363a972add5b8cf8a9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-07-03%2F128084-853308.jpg&h=29b85081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭寒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51b729943c993317c79005fb5b8d0fca49cb829","tid":2092642,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB